there are no nazi skins in germany... Neo nazis are another stupid american product, just like the sitcom Friends... another fine example of american bullshit...

third and final movie, tupac resurrection... its a documentary on tupacs life... waht was interesting was that the whole cocumentary was narrated by him, nd it only just came out. now considering some of the things he said on the movie, and that he's been dead for ard 7 years, this is a really smart guy. should watch it for yourselves...


more news...

hopefully i can get more time here..

it suddenly occured to me that ill be stuck here for only four months more... this is where time starts to speed up a little bit. where you find yourself rushing to do things, and not waiting for the next week, or day...
it was not supposed to end up like that... i was supposed to stay here till i get sick of this place, then beg to be sent back.... looks like its happening too slowly. hopefully things will change in the next 4 months.

im going to miss this place....

now what the fuck is wrong with you people, do you really need to piss me off this way!!is 41 replies about feet an fucking fingers really neccesary? you all are fucking morons.... you really are...  its not funny anymore.. its not cute... its FUCKING ANNOYING!! i officialy hate you people... you people should just burn in hell for wasting my email space....

fuck you all man.....
the last time i was so pissed off by email was when some mega fucker wrote to the email circle about insurance sales techniqes. and guess fucking what? it was from the sam yahoo group as this one i'm ranting about now...i have never beeen so pissed-off by spam or other shit in my email b4.. i guess its because with spam, at least you dont know these people. you didn't associate with them, they came to find you. now with these guys, i am actualy guilty of knowing these retards at least once in my life... and very stupidly joining the yahoo group....

so here i am admiting my guilt..... and with guilt comes anger, white hot anger... 


on lighter note.... 
if you really need to find something to go on and on about something, and you happen to choose something more interesting then moving your fingers and fucking toes in the opposite direction, you might actualy get my interest, like this joker over here....

a bacontarian by his defination is, - a person who supplements an otherwise normal diet with large amounts of pork

now this is cool... this is the real deal man... this fellow vegan hater goes on and on about eating pork.... 
okie its not that interesting but i sure as hell beats fingers and toes...
